# Medium Article – Day 03

## Title:  
The Hidden Engine Behind BubuVerse: Energy, Shards & Player Value

## Summary:  
In this article, I dive into the core mechanics of BubuVerse’s economy.  
I explain how Starlight Energy, Energy Shards, and Bubu progression work together to power the in-game economy.  
This piece explores the balance between energy accumulation, shard usage, and how long-term players can convert their effort into real value.  
It also discusses how these mechanics support a sustainable game design without relying on purely speculative tokenomics.

